1. *Članak* je objavljen u novinama. (The article was published in the newspaper.)
2. *Članaka* je bilo na temu istorije. (The articles were about history.)
3. Izabrao je *članak* koji je smatrao najzanimljivijim. (He chose the article he considered the most interesting.)
4. Čitaoci su se složili da je *članak* bio koristan. (The readers agreed that the article was useful.)
5. Čitajući *članak*, shvatio je da mu je potreban dodatni izvor. (Reading the article, he realized he needed an additional source.)
6. *Članci* su se pojavili u tiskanim medijima. (The articles appeared in printed media.)